snippet.title: Deep Sleep: Labyrinth of the Forsaken - Official Exclusive Gameplay Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description: Take a look at the new trailer for the adventure horror game Deep Sleep Labyrinth of the Forsaken. Embark on a chilling, point-and-click journey through a labyrinth of dreams, solving intricate puzzles and facing nightmarish horrors. Deep Sleep Labyrinth of the Forsaken is coming to PC at a later date.
